INSTALLATION

Install maven and scala
apt-get maven2 scala

Follow these instructions
http://maven.apache.org/guides/getting-started/index.html#How_do_I_make_my_first_Maven_project
http://scala-tools.org/mvnsites/maven-scala-plugin/usage.html
http://www.scalanlp.org/?page_id=6

Download everything and test using the following commands
mvn compile
mvn test
mvn package
mvn clean
mvn java:run
mvn scala:compile scala:run

SOURCES

Labeled Movie Review Data: http://www.cs.cornell.edu/people/pabo/movie-review-data/
MySQL stop words: http://www.koders.com/c/fid6C772BFE1925D9797AD84213004ABB198FC41069.aspx?s=crc
RankNL StopWords: http://www.ranks.nl/resources/stopwords.html
Porter Stemming Algorithm: http://tartarus.org/martin/PorterStemmer/scala.txt 
